title: Celebrate 2nd Anniversary Of Pokemon Duel With Bonuses
body:
Celebrate 2nd Anniversary Of Pokemon Duel With Bonuses

To commemorate the second anniversary of the English-language version of Pokémon Duel, the mobile strategy game in which fans battle each other with digital Pokémon figures, the countdown to the release of the massive Z-Powered Update has begun. More details regarding this mysterious update are coming soon, but it will involve the Legendary Pokémon, Necrozma!  

Fans can claim a trove of items…

My name is Circe and I am the ex leader of the Mossdeep Gym in the Hoenn region, and the aunt of the current Mossdeep gym leaders, Liza and Tate.

I currently work at the Pokémon center with nurse Joy helping rehabilitate sick and injured Pokémon. Any questions you have I am more than willing to answer to the best of my ability
